{"tid":1103550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食Pizza加菠蘿既人都癡線","createTime":"2019-04-12T13:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T14:38:15.000Z","uid":239829,"like":100,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c12626901785b38f51283eff5c2cea31f3c71d","tid":1103550,"uid":239829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"今日同班friend去咗間餐廳食pizza，見到隔離枱有條友係超市買定一包菠蘿，等食pizza既時候放上去一齊食<br />\n<br />\n我啲friend覺得咁樣做唔係好出奇，得我覺得條友痴痴地線，我完全接受唔到pizza上面有菠蘿<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪得我一個覺得好怪，pizza根本同菠蘿唔啱味道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Pizza 根本唔應該有菠蘿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Pizza 加菠蘿好正常"},{"pid":"6c411208bac86d2c41c8bd46501ec4b678964f2a","tid":1103550,"uid":247518,"like":17,"dislike":8,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"正喎波蘿  食落個pizza會無咁油膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed654b29c08a07efb1251246012a5ab098f55cd","tid":1103550,"uid":21149,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"梳 食開菠蘿加pizza"},{"pid":"25b8b641d7d9f681be04593181f6d266d206a057","tid":1103550,"uid":181819,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"唔好扮哂野啦 人講你又講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b659d3ca3bb65bd6152550fbb7fd5e9abe57852","tid":1103550,"uid":17531,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"489b048c4ede78e9cd339e923e79cfc12b3b849b","tid":1103550,"uid":114484,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"食pizza會揀最多菠蘿果塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd830e7f50b3dd430af6da51451b16820cba771","tid":1103550,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔不可偏食<img src=\"/a